Just simply run after you day by day.

39:12.325 --> 39:13.647
God, for that we give you the praise.

39:13.747 --> 39:18.352
Lord, I pray for the month of March that when we talk about revival, it would be clear.

39:18.472 --> 39:19.634
We talk about salvation.

39:19.694 --> 39:20.354
It will be clear.

39:20.675 --> 39:21.716
We talk about impact.

39:21.756 --> 39:22.377
It will be clear.

39:22.837 --> 39:25.700
Not because of Thomas Road and not because of any person in this room.

39:26.481 --> 39:28.503
Lord, but because of you, because of your word.

39:29.965 --> 39:30.866
We pray.

39:31.010 --> 39:32.392
It would not return.

39:33.775 --> 39:35.317
Lord, in advance, we give you the praise.

39:35.558 --> 39:36.680
And Jesus, same we pray.

39:37.962 --> 39:38.302
Amen.

39:39.525 --> 39:42.029
Again, as you leave today, our altar remains open.

39:42.069 --> 39:43.852
You can pick up the bags as you leave.

39:43.912 --> 39:45.675
Don't forget, pick them up.

39:45.755 --> 39:47.658
If you've not signed up, good news.

39:48.320 --> 39:49.281
You can do so today.

39:49.321 --> 39:54.550
They'll do it right on the spot and you can go out of here and we can make an impact together.

39:54.951 --> 39:55.572
God bless you.

39:56.033 --> 39:56.754
Have a great day.

40:00.002 --> 40:01.624
Thank you for worshiping with us today.

40:01.704 --> 40:03.427
We're so glad that you've joined us.

40:04.088 --> 40:07.273
If you prayed to receive Christ today, we'd love to hear from you.

40:08.054 --> 40:11.278
We want to help you as you begin your new faith journey in Christ.

40:11.619 --> 40:16.206
Simply send an email to pastor at trbc.org.

40:16.226 --> 40:27.602
If you've never accepted God's free gift of salvation, the forgiveness of sins made possible by the death and resurrection of Jesus, you can do that today by simply asking Him to save you.

40:27.938 --> 40:30.321
If you'd like to know more, we're here to help you.

40:30.622 --> 40:33.766
Just reach out to us and we'll provide you with some next steps.

40:34.487 --> 40:41.878
Here at Thomas Road, our mission is to change our world by developing Christ followers who love God and love people.

40:42.319 --> 40:49.990
If you'd like to help us fulfill that mission by giving to our ministry, go to trbc.org and make your contribution today.

40:50.591 --> 40:55.698
Your gifts make it possible for us to share the life-changing message of God's love.

